{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2337409, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 447445, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "666 求分享学习技巧", "timestamp": 1629681072, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337774, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447445, "reply_to": 2337409, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我入门是用的标准日本语初级，把语法和单词啥的都掌握的比较熟练，这部分是疫情在家的时候搞的，比较摸鱼，大概花了半年这样，按照单元的数量安排一下学习进度；同时会上https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/easy/看看新闻；读完标日初级之后我有买中级，不过学的比较粗，基本就是读几遍课文，然后随便看看语法；然后ios上有一个叫Japanese的日语辞典应用，里面有背N1-N5单词的功能，平时可以过一下，我感觉考N2前能把N2的单词过一半以上就差不多了；听力方面nhk有个radio，https://www.nhk.or.jp/radio/，我在考试前半年有开始听，不过也就是听个大概，很多听不懂；考试前2-3个月可以去找或者买N2历年原题做一下，可以熟悉一下试卷的结构和难度，而且我感觉今年的N2考了好几道原题。。。", "timestamp": 1629686022, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2338575, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447445, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "kls？", "timestamp": 1629694406, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2339286, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1896, "w": 1644}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 447445, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同乐！", "timestamp": 1629700716, "type": "image", "url": "oq/oqijd2q7z52tz2qaeblnwfllsoa3zsna.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2339557, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447445, "reply_to": 2339286, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 🎊", "timestamp": 1629703091, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 41, "pid": 447445, "reply": 5, "tag": null, "text": "N2考了个满分😂", "timestamp": 1629680891, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629703090, "url": "", "vote": {}}}